Porterfield Lending Solutions (PLS), founded in 2013 by Larry D Porterfield, operates as an Small Business Administration (SBA) Lender Service Provider (LSP).
PLS focuses on guiding lenders when their borrowers stop paying their loans and move into liquidation status.
PLS will prepare or review the Universal Purchase Package (UPP) to request the SBA to honor their guaranty when loans will not be repaid in full
PLS will prepare or review the Care and Preservation of Collateral (CPC) expenses tabs and the Charge-Off Report / Wrap Up Report when all collection actions are complete
PLS will prepare or review the Liquidation Plan tabs or the Litigation Plan tabs 
